column5: Pictures of few steels I got few weeks ago.      Been doing good... Not as good as last year but still good. I guess it's time war. Some times I find a good hole with few right in there but due to the lack of water + gin clear water, they will not bite unless I fish really early.
Beauty pics man!! nice looking chrome you got there!  G.
nice lookin fish !!!  thanks for the candy,..cant wait for that rain a comin!!!
Those are a couple horses. That just helped with the motivation to be out at dawn tomorrow. stupid -7C...  Good work!
nice pics of the steellies. Hoping to get out soon myself, good job.
Nice fish! Under those conditions try fishing at night with a glow stick on your float...
that second fish is a pig!  congrats man.
Wow, I can only dream about getting one as big as the 2nd one! Nice!
Great fish!!!  I'm happy with ones even half that size....LOL.
Some solid fish there!!  It's good to put a face to the name too! Thanks again for the help at the clean-up.  Things should heat up be next weekend, fishing-wise.
Nice steelhead !!!!! and great pics too !!!!   love those fall colors...cheers
Thank you! Can't wait to go out again! Waiting for snow and more water!
